node.title: Woman missing in Queenstown located
node.description: A 39-year-old woman reported missing in the Queenstown area since 31 December was found safe and well last night.
node.content:
["A 39-year-old woman reported missing in the Queenstown area since 31 December was found safe and well last night.", "", "
Jessica Stall was last seen about midday on 31 December Photo: SUPPLIED
", "Police had asked the public to contact them if they have seen Jessica Stall, or the car she may have been driving.", "When the appeal for information was issued on Tuesday police said they were concerned for her safety.", "The police have thanked the public for their assistance."]
